{
 "translations": [
  {
   "offset": 8,
   "len": 12,
   "en": "a young lad.",
   "zh": "一個年輕的少年。",
   "note": "DESC"
  },
  {
   "offset": 31,
   "len": 23,
   "en": "\"A good $T to you, $G.\"",
   "zh": "「$G，$T好。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 63,
   "len": 34,
   "en": "\"Is there more I can do for thee?\"",
   "zh": "「還有什麼吾能為汝效勞的嗎？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 98,
   "len": 25,
   "en": "\"What can I do for thee?\"",
   "zh": "「吾能為汝做什麼？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 130,
   "len": 30,
   "en": "\"What else can I do for thee?\"",
   "zh": "「還有什麼吾能為汝做的？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 168,
   "len": 23,
   "en": "\"Be more specific, $G.\"",
   "zh": "「請說得更具體些，$G。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 194,
   "len": 40,
   "en": "\"Me master 'as quite a large inventory.\"",
   "zh": "「俺主人的存貨相當豐富。」",
   "note": "cockney/working class; 'me' for 'my'"
  },
  {
   "offset": 237,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"Dost thou want @arms or @armor?\"",
   "zh": "「汝要@arms（武器）還是@armor（護甲）？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 288,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"Come to me shop when it's open!\"",
   "zh": "「俺店開門時來光顧！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 353,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"Come to me shop when it's open!\"",
   "zh": "「俺店開門時來光顧！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 418,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"Come to me shop when it's open!\"",
   "zh": "「俺店開門時來光顧！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 468,
   "len": 85,
   "en": "\"I'm just the @apprentice, but if you want to @buy or @sell somethin' I can help ya.\"",
   "zh": "「俺只是個@apprentice（學徒），但若汝想@buy（買）或@sell（賣）麼，俺可以幫汝。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 564,
   "len": 44,
   "en": "\"Me master went off to fight the gargoyles.\"",
   "zh": "「俺主人去對抗魔像族了。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 611,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"'E ain't been 'eard from since.\"",
   "zh": "「打那以後就沒了他的消息。」",
   "note": "h-dropping speech"
  },
  {
   "offset": 647,
   "len": 47,
   "en": "\"I'm just mindin' the place 'til 'e gets back.\"",
   "zh": "「俺只是在看守店舖，等他回來。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 705,
   "len": 22,
   "en": "\"Me name's James, $G.\"",
   "zh": "「俺叫詹姆士，$G。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 743,
   "len": 46,
   "en": "\"Good $T to ya, and I 'ope ye come back soon!\"",
   "zh": "「祝汝$T好，希望汝快快再來！」",
   "note": "bye"
  },
  {
   "offset": 794,
   "len": 17,
   "en": "\"Beg pardon, $G?\"",
   "zh": "「$G，請問汝說什麼？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 955,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"Sorry, none of you has anything I need.\"",
   "zh": "「抱歉，汝等無人有俺需要的東西。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1031,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"Aye, $Y has something of interest...\"",
   "zh": "「嗯，$Y 有俺感興趣的東西……」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1131,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝等哪一位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1368,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "\"Which item?\" ",
   "zh": "「哪件物品？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1460,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"Will you take #7 gold for that $0, $Y?\" ",
   "zh": "「$Y，汝願意以 #7 枚金幣賣那件 $0 嗎？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1514,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Perhaps some other time, then.\"",
   "zh": "「那或許改天再說。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1554,
   "len": 30,
   "en": "\"Perhaps something else then?\"",
   "zh": "「那有其他東西嗎？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1600,
   "len": 52,
   "en": "\"Done!\" $N hands $Y #7 gold pieces and takes the $0.",
   "zh": "「成交！」$N 給 $Y #7 枚金幣，取走 $0。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1708,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"Changed your mind, eh?\"",
   "zh": "「改主意了，嗯？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1820,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝等哪一位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1986,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "\"Which item?\" ",
   "zh": "「哪件物品？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2068,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"That $1 costs #1 gold.\"",
   "zh": "「$1 售價 #1 枚金幣。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2095,
   "len": 18,
   "en": "\"Interested, $Y?\" ",
   "zh": "「有意嗎，$Y？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2156,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"But 'twould make thee o'erburdened, $Y!\"",
   "zh": "「但那會讓汝行李過重，$Y！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2247,
   "len": 12,
   "en": "\"Excellent!\"",
   "zh": "「甚好！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2261,
   "len": 48,
   "en": "After accepting $Y's gold, $N hands over the $1.",
   "zh": "收下 $Y 的金幣後，$N 遞出 $1。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2318,
   "len": 36,
   "en": "\"But thou hast not enough gold, $Y!\"",
   "zh": "「但汝的金幣不足，$Y！」",
